title: Hillsong Worship - Open Heaven / River Wild Full DVD 2015
description:
Open Heaven / River Wild (stylized as OPEN HEAVEN / River Wild) is the 24th annual live worship album by Hillsong. It was recorded during the Hillsong Conference in Sydney, Australia by the Hillsong Worship and UNITED teams last July 2015.
